{
  "stem": "7177.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And would read my mother her fashion shows that she would know what was going on in the world.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But mainly it was done-- my sister had such poor eyesight that she couldn't read or read very little, and she had to know what was going on in the world also.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So that's how we were brought up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The story, the, the home life was unbelievable beautiful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We also had-- my parents were born in 1882, '81 and '82.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had boxes full of books, because my father was a member of a book club.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't think there are that many people who have-- at that time who were members of book clubs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But you know, so if I see now articles about people-- like last week in the they had articles about people who were almost close to 100 years old, they did exactly the same thing that I did, only they-- I mean, I did it at a younger age.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was a beautiful life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I went to school till I was about 15 or 16.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then for-- I think I was 16.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I have to tell you one thing, that during that time, it's coming closer to the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had so much-- so many people in Germany that were related to me, that the war didn't come to me in 1940 like it did the rest of Holland.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To me personally, in our household, the war came to us in 1934, I would say, 1933, when I was still going to Germany for the weekends and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember distinctly in 1933 when I was-- went to Essen, I saw a gentleman, Jewish gentleman, with two little girls who were about my age.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were twins.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
